<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Location — CreatorPort</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;900&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    :root {
      --ink: #181310;
      --ink-soft: #7A736A;
      --ink-faint: #B7AFA4;
      --line: #D6D0C6;
      --page-bg: #FBFAF8;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      background: var(--page-bg);
      color: var(--ink);
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    .page-wrap {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: clamp(80px, 12vw, 120px) clamp(20px, 5vw, 40px) 40px;
    }

    .page-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .32em;
      color: var(--ink-soft);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .page-title {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -.02em;
      color: var(--ink);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .address {
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.15rem);
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--ink);
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .directions {
      font-size: clamp(.9rem, 2vw, 1rem);
      color: var(--ink-soft);
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .facts {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .facts li {
      font-size: clamp(.85rem, 1.8vw, .95rem);
      color: var(--ink);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .facts li::before {
      content: '\2713\00a0\00a0';
      color: #42A6A5;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .map-frame {
      width: 100%;
      height: 320px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .map-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 28px;
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      font-size: .9rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: .04em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #FFFFFF;
      background: var(--ink);
      transition: background .2s ease;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .map-btn:hover { background: #2C2520; }

    .photo-placeholder {
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 16/9;
      background: var(--line);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: var(--ink-faint);
      font-size: .85rem;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    /* ── Burger ── */
    .burger {
      position: fixed;
      top: clamp(16px, 4vw, 32px);
      right: clamp(16px, 4vw, 32px);
      z-index: 100;
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: none;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .burger-line {
      display: block;
      width: 28px;
      height: 3px;
      background: var(--ink);
      border-radius: 2px;
      position: relative;
      transition: transform .3s ease, opacity .3s ease;
    }

    .menu-overlay {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: 99;
      background: var(--page-bg);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 32px;
      opacity: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      transition: opacity .3s ease;
    }

    .menu-overlay.open {
      opacity: 1;
      pointer-events: auto;
    }

    .menu-overlay nav {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .menu-link {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--ink);
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: -.02em;
      transition: opacity .2s ease;
    }

    .menu-link:hover { opacity: .5; }

    .menu-legal {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .menu-legal a {
      font-size: .8rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--ink-faint);
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: .04em;
    }

    .menu-legal a:hover { color: var(--ink); }

    .burger.is-open .burger-line { background: transparent; }
    .burger.is-open .burger-line::before,
    .burger.is-open .burger-line::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      width: 28px;
      height: 3px;
      background: var(--ink);
      border-radius: 2px;
    }
    .burger.is-open .burger-line::before { transform: rotate(45deg); }
    .burger.is-open .burger-line::after { transform: rotate(-45deg); }

    /* ── Footer ── */
    .mini-footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 32px 20px;
      font-size: .7rem;
      color: var(--ink-faint);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .mini-footer a {
      color: var(--ink-faint);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .mini-footer a:hover { color: var(--ink); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <button class="burger" aria-label="Menu">
    <span class="burger-line"></span>
  </button>

  <div class="menu-overlay">
    <nav>
      <a class="menu-link" href="/">Home</a>
      <a class="menu-link" href="/location.html">Location</a>
      <a class="menu-link" href="/our-story.html">Our Story</a>
      <a class="menu-link" href="/about-us.html">About Us</a>
      <a class="menu-link" href="/mars-rover.html">EK10</a>
    </nav>
    <div class="menu-legal">
      <a href="/privacy.html">Privacy</a>
      <a href="/terms.html">Terms</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <main class="page-wrap">
    <p class="page-label">Location</p>
    <h1 class="page-title">3 minutes from Sheung Wan MTR</h1>

    <p class="address">19/F Amtel Building, 144–148 Des Voeux Road Central, Hong Kong</p>

    <p class="directions">Take Exit E1 or A1 at Sheung Wan Station, turn right, and walk straight for about 3 minutes. The Amtel Building entrance is on Des Voeux Road. Take the lift to the 19th floor.</p>

    <ul class="facts">
      <li>Air-conditioned classroom on the 19th floor</li>
      <li>Child-friendly toilets on the same floor</li>
      <li>Drop-off from 8:50 am · pick-up at 12:00 noon</li>
    </ul>

    <iframe
      class="map-frame"
      src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d1844.2!2d114.1543809!3d22.2853932!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3404012fa7a50bb7%3A0x90fe171596df3769!2sLEN!5e0!3m2!1sen!2shk!4v1"
      allowfullscreen=""
      loading="lazy"
      referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
      title="Amtel Building location">
    </iframe>

    <a class="map-btn" href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/LEN+%E5%A0%B4%E5%9C%B0%E7%A7%9F%E7%94%A8%E5%8F%8A%E5%95%86%E5%8B%99%E4%BA%A4%E6%B5%81%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94/@22.2853932,114.1543809,17z/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open in Google Maps</a>

  </main>

  <footer class="mini-footer">
    Space of Possibilities Ltd. · Hong Kong · <a href="/privacy.html">Privacy</a> · <a href="/terms.html">Terms</a> · <a href="https://wa.me/85265427963">Contact</a>
  </footer>

<script>
  const burger = document.querySelector('.burger');
  const overlay = document.querySelector('.menu-overlay');
  burger.addEventListener('click', () => {
    const open = overlay.classList.toggle('open');
    burger.classList.toggle('is-open', open);
    document.body.style.overflow = open ? 'hidden' : '';
  });
</script>
<script>
  // WhatsApp click conversion tracking
  document.querySelectorAll('a[href*="wa.me"]').forEach(function(link) {
    link.addEventListener('click', function() {
      gtag('event', 'conversion', {
        'send_to': 'AW-18308725750/WHATSAPP_LABEL_HIER_EINSETZEN'
      });
    });
  });
</script>
</body>
</html>
